You can try this build script https://gist.github.com/johndpope/fc1c2327a4ae255d9c44dda9b67b5288
(just remove the first line cd / if you're not running on docker)

the difference being a git checkout commit

checkout proper version of serving

git checkout 89e9dfbea055027bc31878ee8da66b54a701a746
git submodule update --init --recursive
